node.text:
Now this is a clutch for the books 📚 so many incredible snakes I could not even keep track 😵‍💫 I'm are going to have to do an update video! Wow they just keep getting crazier 🐼 these panda pied babies aren't even the coolest ones here! I can't even believe the ending either 😱 it's amazing how some things just work out 🙌🙏
.
.
.

node.text:
When it’s the camera guy’s birthday you’ve gotta treat him 🎁 so I suited him up to take my place for the day 😂 looks like he still needs some practice 🤷‍♂️ then again I’m pretty sure most would be just as jumpy their first time 😆 I think I’ll stick to saving snake eggs 🥚 and he’ll stick to filming and editing the videos of it 🎥 enjoy this fun IGTV 📺 
.
.
.

node.text:
What will this gigantic tiger eat 😳 I decided to bring a variety to share with one of @docantle’s kids and wow is it amazing to watch the relationship they have 🐅 Tigers are incredible animals both very intelligent and extreme powerful 💪 definitely something I wouldn’t want to do without one of the pros like Doc around 🙌 enjoy this epic IGTV and see if this big boy eats in the order you guess 🤔 
.
.
.

node.text:
It is so hard to decided which vipers are cooler 😆 the rhino vipers in the last unbxing video 📦 or these epic vipers 🐍 which happen to have the longest fangs of any venomous snake in the world 😱 now thats no joke 😬 I'm so happy to have them here at The Zoo to share with all the visitors 🙌 and to educate countless people in person and over the world wide web 📱 
.
.
.

node.text:
Spotted this pile of junk on the side of the road and each time I visited we found some epic rattlesnakes 🐍 this junk serves as an artifical reef for all sorts of animals 🐁🦎🕷 of course never handle rattlesnakes or any venomous snakes like I do 🚫 it is a good idea to never bother any wild snake as you may never know if it is venomous or not 🤷‍♂️ better safe than sorry!
.
.
.
#reptile #snake #rattlesnake #venomous #animals #viper #herping #wildlife #cool #education #igtv #igtvchannel #video #style

node.text:
Bubbles the elephant has such an amazing story 🤩 she was an orphan in Africa until @docantle rescued her 😳 and the rest is history 🤷‍♂️ she has since educated countless people 🐘 I was an orphan too and it’s amazing what I’ve been able to do 🙌🙌 so even if the start is rough remember 💭 you can always make the best of it and even help so many others in the process 🙏 have a great SuperSunday ☀️ and don’t stop Living Your Dream 😎
.
.
.
#animals #elephant #education #orphan #learn #motivation #positivevibes #livingthedream #supersunday #insta #photooftheday #fun
